---
title: Easy As (Shepherd's) Pie with Caramelized Onions and Roasted Carrots
description: Although shepherd’s pie was originally created as a “clean out the refrigerator” dish to use up leftovers, it has morphed into a warm and comforting classic to enjoy any night of the week. After all, what’s not to love about the combination of hearty ground beef, caramelized onions, and a crunchy potato crust?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caramelized-onion-shepherd-s-pie-a3c34747.jpg
